# @param {Integer[]} nums
# @return {Integer}
def minimum_index(nums)
    dominant = nums.max_by { |n| nums.count(n) }
    count = nums.count(dominant)
    left_count = 0
    nums.each_with_index do |num, i|
        left_count += 1 if num == dominant
        right_count = count - left_count
        if left_count * 2 > i + 1 && right_count * 2 > nums.size - i - 1
            return i
        end
    end
    -1
end
